<p>Hi <%= @user&.name %>,</p>
<p>We recently received a request to reset your account password. If you didn't request this, please ignore this email. Your password won't change until you access the link below and create a new one.</p>
<p style = "margin-bottom: 30px;">To change your password, click the following link below:</p>
<div style = "text-align: center;">
  <%= link_to 'CHANGE MY PASSWORD', edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token), class: "sm-mg-5", style: "width: 200px; height: 39px; margin-left:0%; margin-right:0%; padding: 10px 20px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; background: #0782D0; border-radius: 6px; color: white;" %>
</div>
<br>
<p>With gratitude,<br>The Giving Connection Team</p>
